        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 1 of SLEEP: A 30-Day Tapping Intensive. The script meets the exhaustion and frustration of ongoing sleep difficulty where it is, not with reassurance, but with acknowledgement. The point is not to fix the sleep tonight but to clear the charge of the struggle so it doesn't compound itself through the day. Use it during daylight hours, not at bedtime.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to tapping? Read ",
